      • LIST_REGEX

        public static final java.lang.String LIST_REGEX
        Regular expression String representing a list of valid SSC web service library identifier values. Groups 1,3,5,... contain the library name and groups 2,4,6,... contain the programming environment identifier. Note: global case-insensitive matching (?i) was avoided so this regex can be used as part of a larger regex which may not want case-insensitive matches.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
